701131f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 149th Street (East)
701131f-a.text:
Grand Concourse, north from E. 149th Street, showing
the thoroughfare being widened on the west side, A number
of old tenements were razed and several taxpayerg were
erected on the new zoning line. In the background is the
Bronx SSounty Court House.
June 9, 1940
